{"title":"在黄河两岸长城内外","authors":["郭煌"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄河两岸长城内外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄河两岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城内外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收大军把阵势摆开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像面临着征战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人马从千村万户中扑来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀磨亮了三遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道道银光放异彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车辕早就套好了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把一座座金山驮载。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骡马急得扬蹄撒欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦黄鸟已经把羽毛叫白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割机等得撒开腿了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰??向田里开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党支书撑着红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐得直抡胳膊敞开怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们边走边夸："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“看谁收割得又净又快！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}